headline: BC Woman Takes On US Big Tech: Social Platform EH! Adds Web Version to Compete Directly with Facebook
summary: Every year, an estimated $10 billion in Canadian advertising revenue flows to American tech platforms. They employ few Canadians, pay minimal Canadian taxes, and store Canadian data on US-based servers. One woman-led BC company is doing something about it.
